Package com.varukha.webproject.util.report.impl

package com.varukha.webproject.util.report.impl
This package contains methods for create: - payment bill, - report by definite days of cargo delivery, - report by destination deliver city (from/to).
Version:
1.0
Author:
Dmytro Varukha

    Class DeliveryReportByDestinationBuilder used to generate pdf report by destination city by using Itext pdf library.

    Class PaymentBillBuilder it is a type of command that used to generate payment bill by manager in pdf format by using Itext pdf library.

    Class PDFReportByReportType used to select the necessary report generator by type of report from PDFReportFactory to create pdf report.
